description: Retention and refurbishment of the Alfa Laval Building for use as a 180 bed hotel (Class C1) and redevelopment of the site to provide a 151 bed hotel (Class C1), 4,677 sq m class B1 offices, 228sq m retail/community use (Class A1/D1), 206 flats, maisonettes and houses (Class C3), together withassociated public and private open space, access,service areas, plant, landscaping and 351 car prking spaces. The buildings range from 2-12 storeys in height.
